{
  "description": "A vibrant image capturing a harbor scene at dusk or dawn. The sky is ablaze with warm hues of orange and red, transitioning to a deep blue overhead. A long pier or industrial waterfront is visible, dotted with lights and structures, including what appears to be a large container crane. The water is disturbed by a wake, creating radiating lines of light that reflect the colors of the sky. The wake suggests a vessel has recently passed through, and white foam traces the edges of the waves. The composition is dominated by the water and sky, creating a sense of expansive space and tranquility.  A Maersk container is visible in the foreground. ",
